data.description: Sellers motivated and considering all reasonable offers, schedule your showing today! This beautiful home is located in the desirable neighborhood of Sterling Lakes featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a large family room. An office space is located off the foyer. Main level master suite with a master bath that includes double vanities and a separate shower. Hardwoods throughout the main level.Kitchen features granite countertops and additional pantry space. A sunroom is the perfect addition at the rear of the home. Upstairs features 2 bedrooms and a large bonus room. The scenic views of this area are vastly unique and the location of this home makes commuting suitable to the surrounding areas. With this home being located conveniently in unincorporated Helena with easy access to Helena, Exit 6 onto I459, highway 150 in Hoover and McCalla. Approximately a 7 minute drive to Publix on South Shades Crest Rd and 15 minutes away from the new UAB Medical West facility opening in 2024.
